{"tid":403580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"休班女警袁樂欣，酒醉後襲擊侍應","createTime":"2017-09-17T10:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:54:55.000Z","uid":89349,"like":6,"dislike":141,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"253cd502263d88f16686f37480b11c48589dec0d","tid":403580,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:03:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/180148_df2b024980b079fa24eaac01e1c07b33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F180148_df2b024980b079fa24eaac01e1c07b33.jpg&h=38d9b0d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n休班女警醉酒後在街頭襲擊兩名不相識的女侍應，早前經審訊後女警被裁定罪成及判社會服務令。<br />\n<br />\n其中日夜兼兩職的女侍應因被襲擊致<span style=\"color: red;\">腰椎受傷</span>，未能上班兩個月，故今入稟小額錢債審裁處向女警追討3.2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n惟由於女警事後已辭職，警方未肯透露女警聯絡地址，女侍應未能將法庭文件送達被告，案件押後至11月13日再訊，待女侍應找尋女警地址。女侍應在庭外稱會向區議員求助。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"b1494a26b4ddde77d68353b30ecb3b1a4949ae1b","tid":403580,"uid":50744,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"壼～型撚到"},{"pid":"9729a5819581c575c205a1fc0282d79ed830efb1","tid":403580,"uid":2949,"like":51,"dislike":1,"score":50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:06:54.000Z","msg":"黑警真係黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6deb7336461d14c949899522296ddbd3e18466","tid":403580,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:07:29.000Z","msg":"屌佢老母因住比人起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b517157b731100ed553649fbae299655bcc7fe53","tid":403580,"uid":4052,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T10:07:39.000Z","msg":"成個泡菜明星咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d281f6ee982cbace2f5001ca7